description: Dr. Nor is a physician in Emporium. He`s a good friend of Honoka`s, despite the fact that he drives her crazy with his poking and prodding about her love-life. Nor is intelligent, sincere, carefree, and rather irresponsible - it`d be a stretch to call him a medical "professional" - but he certainly is good at what he does.
name: Nor
